game_description: This game is a multiplayer adventure game with mixture of VR and physical gamebook-like cards. This game requires Oculus Quest/Quest2 application AND physical print of the game.
review_1: I hear a ding noise once a while after waiting up to 1 min.
review_2: I need to put in some code and its in Japanese
review_3: I'm very confused on what this game truly is, there seems to be no footage of the game either, there is just a input screen for a four digit code which seems privately for admin players. But the cover looks kinda cool.
